Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個與命運持續戰鬥著的男人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.64,0:01:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙一行人 在和阿蒂妮的海戰中取得了勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那場戰鬥中 陽子明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮亞信賴著自己 信賴著大Gurren團這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子對妮亞的不信任也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大Gurren團的羈絆變得更深了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 你在這兒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎? 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想 妮亞怎麼給人印象徹底變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪 一點都不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想和你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家都在忙著工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人什麼都不做 這種事我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想做點什麼 給大家幫點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但妮亞是公主嘛 只要這樣微笑著...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是公主了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也 也對呢...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你又從早上開始什麼都沒吃?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃的時候我也吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能開動Lagann的只有你一個 有個萬一的時候怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃也是工作之一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃也是工作之一?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 打擾到你們了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也找到答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(痛 痛痛痛 痛啊痛啊痛啊!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 西蒙借我一用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 長不大的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第13話 大家多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅修他怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因不明 但看起來身體沒什麼異狀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是積勞過度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還是小孩子 卻要駕駛Gurren不斷戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒下也難怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也沒資格說別人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近是不是有點努力過頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 只是在幹我該幹的事罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能吃到超~豪華的料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼拚命的妮亞也好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是從昨天起就絕食在等著了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你那也太過火了吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你打算吃多少啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮亞說她也想工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 馬上好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那點很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然從大小來看應該是戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但顯示的坐標指向空中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷達沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是敵人真的從天上來的話 要怎麼回擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,262)\fs18\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\shad0\bord1\b1}飛行要塞航母型GUNMEN 大GUNTEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了展示我的力量的時刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋王羅傑諾姆 請好好看著吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體突擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是羅修的代理哦 Gurren由我來駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來有什麼不滿嗎? 我也有好好訓練哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜塔?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜塔?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意和我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不攻過來嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了! 來啊來啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來決一勝負嗎 勝負!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「紅葉」接近中!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記著!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事可不會再有下次了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gurren-Lagann!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好弱 太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是群葬送了齊米魯夫和阿蒂妮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓古阿姆都顏面掃地的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為有多強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是他們太弱 是我太強了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達雅卡 Gurren-Lagann要出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出去也只是給他們當靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 再把我們扔出去 利朧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒空囉囉嗦嗦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成怎樣我都不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 看來能把它收為己用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 看來能行!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣和飛行戰艦也能一戰了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能幹啊 那兩個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇悠和奇亞露嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 10倍報復
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來幫忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 可要吃不到妮亞做的大餐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大餐! 大餐!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就讓他們看看大Gurren團的鬥志吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:10:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反擊~開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一口氣衝上去了哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方GANMEN 高速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還能相見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見啊 光屁股猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉魯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白嗎 我的無念!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人苟活下來的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了和你一戰而低聲下氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加了今天這場戰鬥的我的心情!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 還不能熟練控制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不會吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不了的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉魯 和敵方GANMEN一起撞入飛行球控制室中!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 算不了什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有小孩和女人在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那在哪兒!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥他..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥他..已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候..就死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那他..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說我是 輸給了你嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 一個人..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子 我會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了之後 把戴著受傷的人當作藉口的話 我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANMEN欠下的東西 就用GANMEN來還吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的作風!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前飛行球動力下降中! 無法維持高度!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼啊 維拉魯!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他們那邊在冒煙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會啊 我們上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也被打得很慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮全部損壞 動力室也快成破爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰管這種事啊 西蒙他們可是在敵人肚子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不掩護他們的話又該怎麼辦啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我飛過去把他們全踢飛!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句話收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼區區一個人類小孩!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此做個了結吧 維拉魯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 真的一個人也能戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,262)\fs18\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\shad0\bord1\b1}西托曼多拉專用特化GANMEN SHEZAKKU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動 那邊的GANMEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢動的話 這隻母猴子就要變成肉餅了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西托曼多拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算玩到什麼時候 維拉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不聽什麼藉口 給他最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 西蒙 戰鬥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好卑鄙啊 維拉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次每次 這就是你的作風嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利朧 這麼做真的沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就行了 讓我推吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我 吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大Gurren 最大戰速!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 這算什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能以這種方式和那個人類做了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瘋了嗎 維拉魯!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你撿回來的恩情 看來你也忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉魯!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛踢啊 飛踢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了完了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 只是擦了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子 沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是呢 是卜塔保護了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 看來那個就是飛行的動力源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 把那個抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的飛行球被奪走了 飛行機能已經無法維持!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法撐住!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉魯 可不會那麼簡單就饒了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後退中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算把他們趕回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 西蒙 知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 喜歡卡米那哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭和內臟沒異常呢 靜養一段時間就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太結實也讓人頭痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 利朧說得太誇張了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個問題 剛才做好的飯菜 大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了嘛 吃也是工作之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 還會再來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅修?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實..是昨天的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然被妮亞拜託試吃她做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 實在沒法想像是這世界的東西的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對看來很高興的在做菜的妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能明白地跟她說不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果就把所有菜都試吃了..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個才..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的失敗 全是因為這傢伙違反命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又無能又喜歡反抗 簡直是個沒救的蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必 將維拉魯處以極刑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋王 如果您命令我死的話 我甘願受死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前有事想請您告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 維拉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真的是比獸人低劣的生物嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類..到底是什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HO..西托曼多拉 你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這男人就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獸人還真是不完全的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那巨人為了維持肉體 如同死一般的沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在此期間進行的細胞的再生是必不可缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:22:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是硬要醒過來的話 全身的細胞就會壞死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生產出獸人的是螺旋王您
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對這種肉體..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那答案 你真的想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉魯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多厚的牆都有崩潰的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此堅信著向前衝 和同伴們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 天元突破Gurren-Lagann
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位貴安